//     â”‚           - Manage doctors & patients
//     â”‚           - View reports
//     â”‚           - Cannot manage other admins
//     â”‚
// DOCTOR â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€ Healthcare provider
//     â”‚           - View own patients
//     â”‚           - Manage appointments
//     â”‚           - Write prescriptions
